"To open the <span class=\"filename\">Persistent</span> folder, choose\n"
"<span class=\"menuchoice\">\n"
"  <span class=\"guimenu\">Places</span>&nbsp;▸\n"
"  <span class=\"guimenuitem\">Home Folder</span></span>, and open the <span\n"
